WEBVTT

00:01:35.860 --> 00:01:38.270
[Too Young To Love]

00:01:38.460 --> 00:01:41.270
[Episode 18]

00:01:45.500 --> 00:01:48.160
What is your relationship
with Professor Zhao?

00:01:50.390 --> 00:01:52.720
It's a professor-student relationship.

00:01:52.759 --> 00:01:54.360
You're stating the obvious!

00:01:55.130 --> 00:01:56.280
I didn't call you here

00:01:56.280 --> 00:01:58.120
to watch me get beaten up.

00:01:58.750 --> 00:01:59.860
Can you just let me make things clear?

00:01:59.860 --> 00:02:01.480
This won't solve anything.

00:02:01.740 --> 00:02:03.730
Who do you think you are?

00:02:04.550 --> 00:02:07.610
You just stood there taking pictures
instead of helping me.

00:02:07.610 --> 00:02:09.530
If these photos aren't good enough,

00:02:09.530 --> 00:02:10.770
don't bother coming in tomorrow.

00:02:10.770 --> 00:02:11.280
Oh.

00:02:11.740 --> 00:02:13.200
Mr. Ma, please take a look.

00:02:25.110 --> 00:02:26.460
Terrible shot!

00:02:26.480 --> 00:02:27.210
Not this one.

00:02:27.230 --> 00:02:28.060
There are more.

00:02:28.060 --> 00:02:29.220
Keep flipping.

00:02:38.670 --> 00:02:40.000
Send this one to me.

00:02:42.400 --> 00:02:44.260
I'll send it to you when I get back.

00:02:45.600 --> 00:02:46.410
Mr. Ma,

00:02:47.140 --> 00:02:50.420
should I step in
if you get beaten up again?

00:02:52.250 --> 00:02:53.280
Of course!

00:02:54.060 --> 00:02:55.620
If we run into this again,

00:02:55.640 --> 00:02:57.270
you step up first.

00:02:58.130 --> 00:02:58.750
Okay.

00:02:59.960 --> 00:03:01.470
Your composition

00:03:01.490 --> 00:03:02.560
is pretty good.

00:03:05.020 --> 00:03:06.370
Call me Ma from now on.

00:03:08.230 --> 00:03:09.830
Are you free tomorrow night?

00:03:10.380 --> 00:03:11.620
I have no plans yet.

00:03:13.770 --> 00:03:15.570
There is an interview tomorrow.

00:03:15.610 --> 00:03:16.540
You come with me.

00:03:16.900 --> 00:03:18.700
I'll send you the address later.

00:03:19.100 --> 00:03:19.670
Okay.

00:03:19.770 --> 00:03:20.770
Thank you, Mr. Ma.

00:03:21.900 --> 00:03:22.750
Thank you, Ma.

00:03:55.520 --> 00:03:58.240
Xiaole, we've made up with Chen Zhihan.

00:03:58.260 --> 00:04:00.320
See you at the sports ground tonight.

00:04:23.240 --> 00:04:24.080
So,

00:04:25.150 --> 00:04:26.270
how was your year

00:04:26.410 --> 00:04:26.890
abroad?

00:04:27.040 --> 00:04:28.170
Just so-so.

00:04:29.540 --> 00:04:31.980
We had exams every single month.

00:04:32.200 --> 00:04:33.610
I always came in last.

00:04:34.940 --> 00:04:35.940
Last?

00:04:36.130 --> 00:04:36.810
Seriously?

00:04:36.840 --> 00:04:38.640
I remember you were pretty good.

00:04:38.790 --> 00:04:40.150
I am pretty good,

00:04:40.570 --> 00:04:42.230
but everyone else is good too.

00:04:42.750 --> 00:04:45.020
At first I practiced 3 hours a day.

00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:46.610
Then 5 hours.

00:04:46.840 --> 00:04:47.550
In the end,

00:04:48.070 --> 00:04:50.400
I practically lived in the practice room.

00:04:51.900 --> 00:04:52.590
That

00:04:52.610 --> 00:04:53.810
must have been tough.

00:05:01.680 --> 00:05:02.510
How about you?

00:05:04.210 --> 00:05:05.020
I...

00:05:07.050 --> 00:05:07.850
Same old.

00:05:09.170 --> 00:05:10.630
What does "same old" mean?

00:05:11.790 --> 00:05:12.790
You know,

00:05:13.560 --> 00:05:15.840
just fixing instruments, going to work,

00:05:16.150 --> 00:05:17.150
running the shop,

00:05:18.010 --> 00:05:19.270
and teaching lessons.

00:05:20.530 --> 00:05:22.930
I don't really like the life
I'm living now.

00:05:23.210 --> 00:05:26.140
I don't want
to teach at a university forever either.

00:05:27.110 --> 00:05:30.310
I'm applying to be the principal cellist
of an orchestra.

00:05:30.530 --> 00:05:31.410
If I succeed,

00:05:32.840 --> 00:05:35.300
I'll be able
to travel and perform with them.

00:05:47.090 --> 00:05:47.550
Come on.

00:05:47.770 --> 00:05:48.630
Please come in.

00:05:49.450 --> 00:05:51.010
How's the sunset?

00:05:51.770 --> 00:05:52.570
Beautiful.

00:05:52.650 --> 00:05:53.530
In the future,

00:05:53.720 --> 00:05:56.280
we'll put a small sofa right here.

00:05:56.280 --> 00:05:57.260
We'll sit here,

00:05:57.450 --> 00:05:59.700
basking in the sunlight.

00:05:59.730 --> 00:06:00.980
And right here,

00:06:01.090 --> 00:06:03.890
we've got to have a vinyl record player.

00:06:03.890 --> 00:06:04.970
Just imagine, every night,

00:06:04.970 --> 00:06:06.170
after we have dinner,

00:06:06.210 --> 00:06:07.970
we'll put on some music,

00:06:07.970 --> 00:06:10.390
have a drink,

00:06:10.530 --> 00:06:12.530
and dance a little.

00:06:18.090 --> 00:06:18.720
What do you think?

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:19.450
Sounds good.

00:06:19.660 --> 00:06:20.490
Satisfied?

00:06:20.890 --> 00:06:21.550
Satisfied.

00:06:21.970 --> 00:06:23.500
Good, that's what matters.

00:06:24.330 --> 00:06:24.930
By the way,

00:06:25.660 --> 00:06:27.190
I have good news for you too.

00:06:27.530 --> 00:06:28.330
Just say it.

00:06:28.450 --> 00:06:29.890
Whatever hopes you have for the future,

00:06:29.890 --> 00:06:31.150
I'll fulfill them all.

00:06:31.970 --> 00:06:33.890
My application to study abroad

00:06:33.890 --> 00:06:34.970
got accepted.

00:06:36.720 --> 00:06:37.770
That's good.

00:06:38.450 --> 00:06:41.090
I'll go check the bathroom.
It seems the...

00:06:41.330 --> 00:06:42.060
drainage...

00:06:42.210 --> 00:06:43.090
What's wrong?

00:06:48.210 --> 00:06:49.120
Nothing.

00:06:49.409 --> 00:06:50.409
Just checking.

00:06:50.450 --> 00:06:52.310
There seems to be something wrong

00:06:52.330 --> 00:06:53.770
with the drainage system.

00:06:53.770 --> 00:06:54.970
You're acting weird.

00:07:09.930 --> 00:07:10.880
Can you not go?

00:07:13.650 --> 00:07:15.010
I'll only be gone for 3 years.

00:07:15.010 --> 00:07:16.120
It'll go by fast.

00:07:17.970 --> 00:07:19.010
3 years...

00:07:21.570 --> 00:07:22.530
3 years

00:07:23.530 --> 00:07:25.280
can change a lot of things,

00:07:27.520 --> 00:07:28.720
including you and me.

00:07:29.890 --> 00:07:30.970
You and me?

00:07:31.840 --> 00:07:33.520
How?

00:07:33.650 --> 00:07:34.890
How?

00:07:35.890 --> 00:07:37.020
Fine, I'll tell you.

00:07:38.090 --> 00:07:39.210
For these three years,

00:07:39.210 --> 00:07:40.530
you'll be abroad all alone.

00:07:40.530 --> 00:07:44.460
If you get sick, without me by your side,
who's going to take care of you?

00:07:44.720 --> 00:07:46.010
I'll be here all alone.

00:07:46.010 --> 00:07:47.530
If I get sick, without you by my side,

00:07:47.530 --> 00:07:48.860
what am I supposed to do?

00:07:50.450 --> 00:07:51.650
Don't give me

00:07:52.409 --> 00:07:53.090
that long-distance relationship talk.

00:07:53.090 --> 00:07:55.770
Don't tell me we can still be together
by texting, calling,

00:07:55.770 --> 00:07:57.010
and video chatting every day.

00:07:57.010 --> 00:07:57.570
Let me tell you.

00:07:57.570 --> 00:07:58.650
I don't need that!

00:07:58.720 --> 00:07:59.530
And I don't believe in it!

00:07:59.530 --> 00:08:02.450
All I need is you by my side!
Understand?

00:08:06.450 --> 00:08:08.250
Then you go abroad with me, okay?

00:08:09.210 --> 00:08:10.120
Go with you?

00:08:12.590 --> 00:08:13.910
How can I go with you?

00:08:14.890 --> 00:08:16.280
I've bought a house here.

00:08:16.280 --> 00:08:17.970
My studio is here.

00:08:17.970 --> 00:08:19.530
All my best friends are here.

00:08:19.530 --> 00:08:20.410
How can I go with you?

00:08:20.410 --> 00:08:21.650
What would I even do there?

00:08:21.650 --> 00:08:22.530
What would I do?

00:08:22.530 --> 00:08:24.120
Just be your plus-one?

00:08:24.630 --> 00:08:25.210
I'm tell you

00:08:25.210 --> 00:08:26.330
I can't do it.

00:08:34.880 --> 00:08:35.880
I get it.

00:08:38.850 --> 00:08:39.520
So,

00:08:40.400 --> 00:08:41.210
you

00:08:43.120 --> 00:08:44.090
never actually

00:08:46.640 --> 00:08:49.000
thought about our future, did you?

00:08:56.090 --> 00:08:56.810
It's fine.

00:09:08.450 --> 00:09:09.210
Good.

00:09:09.870 --> 00:09:11.450
Then I wish you the best of luck

00:09:11.450 --> 00:09:12.780
with your application.

00:09:17.690 --> 00:09:19.550
I have things to do. I'm going now.

00:09:19.690 --> 00:09:21.150
What's wrong with you now?

00:09:21.850 --> 00:09:22.850
Nothing.

00:09:23.480 --> 00:09:25.970
I just don't want to be with someone
who has no future with me.

00:09:25.970 --> 00:09:26.770
Is that wrong?

00:09:30.240 --> 00:09:31.500
Let's leave it at that.

00:09:38.850 --> 00:09:39.720
Little Champion,

00:09:39.720 --> 00:09:41.050
have you been waiting long?

00:09:41.050 --> 00:09:42.720
You're finally here.

00:09:44.720 --> 00:09:45.600
Listen,

00:09:45.620 --> 00:09:47.970
I was really happy today.

00:09:47.970 --> 00:09:50.360
Do you remember that gig at the café
back in high school?

00:09:50.360 --> 00:09:52.330
It felt exactly the same.

00:09:52.330 --> 00:09:53.570
Of course I remember.

00:09:53.850 --> 00:09:54.970
I've got good news too.

00:09:54.970 --> 00:09:55.480
Yeah.

00:09:56.450 --> 00:09:58.330
Today, my first day of internship

00:09:58.330 --> 00:09:59.900
went really well.

00:10:01.970 --> 00:10:03.600
Do you still have to practice today?

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:04.480
No.

00:10:04.480 --> 00:10:05.480
Let's go celebrate.

00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:06.330
What do you say?

00:10:06.330 --> 00:10:07.050
Then,

00:10:07.690 --> 00:10:09.020
how are we celebrating?

00:10:10.240 --> 00:10:11.840
We'll eat whatever you want.

00:10:13.850 --> 00:10:15.450
Did your stomach just growl?

00:10:28.600 --> 00:10:30.210
When you were playing just now,

00:10:30.210 --> 00:10:30.970
I noticed

00:10:30.970 --> 00:10:33.810
your wound kept flashing before my eyes.

00:10:34.330 --> 00:10:35.090
To be honest,

00:10:35.720 --> 00:10:36.970
I was really worried.

00:10:37.450 --> 00:10:38.210
Thanks.

00:10:38.570 --> 00:10:40.640
I didn't even notice when I got hurt.

00:10:42.330 --> 00:10:43.170
Looks like

00:10:43.170 --> 00:10:44.240
we're both free.

00:10:44.360 --> 00:10:45.760
How about we have a drink?

00:10:45.930 --> 00:10:47.810
I'm not feeling well today.

00:10:47.930 --> 00:10:49.060
Maybe another time.

00:10:49.600 --> 00:10:50.170
Well,

00:10:50.190 --> 00:10:50.970
I'll get going then.

00:10:50.970 --> 00:10:51.480
Yu.

00:10:52.120 --> 00:10:53.000
I wanted to ask

00:10:53.240 --> 00:10:55.360
about Mr. Guo, whom we met last time.

00:10:55.600 --> 00:10:56.900
What are his conditions

00:10:56.900 --> 00:10:58.700
for sponsoring music students?

00:11:00.860 --> 00:11:01.740
Well,

00:11:03.690 --> 00:11:04.540
I'm not really

00:11:04.600 --> 00:11:05.570
sure about that.

00:11:05.840 --> 00:11:06.700
How about this?

00:11:06.720 --> 00:11:07.930
I'll put in a good word for you,

00:11:07.930 --> 00:11:08.790
ask him nicely,

00:11:08.930 --> 00:11:11.590
and see
if he'll fully fund your studies abroad.

00:11:14.050 --> 00:11:14.720
You

00:11:14.720 --> 00:11:15.720
don't have to feel pressured.

00:11:15.720 --> 00:11:17.520
Take your time to think about it.

00:11:18.150 --> 00:11:18.850
You know,

00:11:18.850 --> 00:11:19.600
our circle

00:11:19.600 --> 00:11:21.450
values educational background

00:11:21.570 --> 00:11:23.030
and experience very much.

00:11:25.930 --> 00:11:26.330
Yeah.

00:11:26.810 --> 00:11:27.450
Thank you.

00:11:30.450 --> 00:11:30.930
Ning.

00:11:31.090 --> 00:11:32.050
How about this?

00:11:32.450 --> 00:11:33.790
I'm pretty close

00:11:33.820 --> 00:11:34.970
with Mr. Guo.

00:11:35.070 --> 00:11:36.680
I'll ask him out,

00:11:36.710 --> 00:11:38.360
and we can have a good talk with him

00:11:38.360 --> 00:11:40.610
about how to generate revenue for him.

00:11:41.720 --> 00:11:43.360
After all, they are businessmen.

00:11:43.360 --> 00:11:44.450
Without profit,

00:11:44.830 --> 00:11:47.110
he won't just sponsor you to go abroad
for nothing.

00:11:47.110 --> 00:11:47.950
Right?

00:11:49.090 --> 00:11:49.570
Yeah.

00:11:50.090 --> 00:11:50.950
How about this?

00:11:51.210 --> 00:11:51.820
Yu.

00:11:51.970 --> 00:11:54.370
Next time you meet Mr. Guo,
take me with you.

00:11:54.480 --> 00:11:55.490
I'll do my best

00:11:55.520 --> 00:11:58.330
to help you secure the investment
for the orchestra.

00:11:58.330 --> 00:11:59.720
And I would really appreciate it

00:11:59.720 --> 00:12:01.380
if you put in a good word for me.

00:12:04.380 --> 00:12:04.880
Okay.

00:12:05.090 --> 00:12:06.330
Wait for my news.

00:12:08.720 --> 00:12:09.180
I'm off.

00:12:09.850 --> 00:12:10.330
Bye.

00:12:23.980 --> 00:12:26.920
So this Ma is quite a character.

00:12:27.320 --> 00:12:29.410
Your job sounds pretty fun.

00:12:29.930 --> 00:12:31.090
It really is fun.

00:12:31.090 --> 00:12:33.530
My head is still spinning from his punch.

00:12:33.850 --> 00:12:34.690
Spinning?

00:12:34.690 --> 00:12:35.450
Let me see.

00:12:35.570 --> 00:12:36.360
Here?

00:12:36.380 --> 00:12:37.010
Yeah.

00:12:37.360 --> 00:12:38.970
There's a big bump!

00:12:38.970 --> 00:12:39.970
Then blow on it.

00:12:41.210 --> 00:12:41.720
Better?

00:12:43.480 --> 00:12:44.470
The bump is gone.

00:12:44.850 --> 00:12:46.030
Wow, magic.

00:12:49.930 --> 00:12:51.600
Do you know what I was thinking

00:12:51.600 --> 00:12:52.810
while I was playing today?

00:12:52.810 --> 00:12:54.140
What were you thinking?

00:12:54.750 --> 00:12:55.480
Let me guess.

00:12:56.360 --> 00:12:57.690
Were you thinking

00:12:58.570 --> 00:13:00.850
about how amazing you actually played?

00:13:00.850 --> 00:13:02.450
Was my playing not good?

00:13:02.590 --> 00:13:03.920
Your playing was great.

00:13:04.450 --> 00:13:07.090
Actually, when the semester started,

00:13:07.170 --> 00:13:09.640
there were so many talented people around.

00:13:09.850 --> 00:13:12.570
Even though I passed
Professor Ye's audition,

00:13:12.990 --> 00:13:14.600
I still felt like I wasn't good enough.

00:13:14.600 --> 00:13:15.450
And now?

00:13:16.330 --> 00:13:17.760
Now I feel

00:13:18.450 --> 00:13:20.380
that at least I'm chasing my dream.

00:13:20.450 --> 00:13:21.870
At least I can

00:13:21.970 --> 00:13:22.810
feel

00:13:23.330 --> 00:13:25.540
and even enjoy every single moment.

00:13:26.050 --> 00:13:27.250
That's enough for me.

00:13:27.970 --> 00:13:29.950
Actually, in this world,

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:31.240
there are

00:13:31.600 --> 00:13:33.050
so many people

00:13:33.330 --> 00:13:35.930
working harder and struggling harder
than us.

00:13:36.850 --> 00:13:37.570
So,

00:13:38.330 --> 00:13:39.570
we're already doing great.

00:13:39.570 --> 00:13:40.170
Yeah.

00:13:42.360 --> 00:13:42.970
To dreams.

00:13:43.170 --> 00:13:44.090
To our dreams.

00:13:44.280 --> 00:13:44.720
To

00:13:44.850 --> 00:13:46.330
our future.

00:13:51.810 --> 00:13:52.740
I almost forgot.

00:13:53.090 --> 00:13:53.800
What?

00:13:53.970 --> 00:13:55.700
The 100-day anniversary gift.

00:13:56.330 --> 00:13:57.810
100-day anniversary?

00:13:57.810 --> 00:13:59.570
I thought it was still a few days away.

00:13:59.570 --> 00:14:01.720
I counted from the day we kissed.

00:14:02.450 --> 00:14:05.510
Shouldn't we count
from the day I confessed?

00:14:05.810 --> 00:14:07.360
Just take it.

00:14:08.570 --> 00:14:09.210
So,

00:14:09.850 --> 00:14:10.640
what is this?

00:14:11.450 --> 00:14:12.720
This is

00:14:12.720 --> 00:14:13.560
our

00:14:13.690 --> 00:14:14.850
love notebook.

00:14:15.170 --> 00:14:16.330
Our love notebook?

00:14:16.720 --> 00:14:18.330
One is for you, and the other is for me.

00:14:18.330 --> 00:14:20.820
If you have something
you want to say to me

00:14:20.930 --> 00:14:23.330
but are too shy to say it,

00:14:23.480 --> 00:14:24.940
just write it down in here.

00:14:26.570 --> 00:14:27.690
Sounds romantic.

00:14:27.690 --> 00:14:29.090
But how do I give it to you?

00:14:29.450 --> 00:14:30.570
Leave it

00:14:30.720 --> 00:14:32.050
under the tree

00:14:32.690 --> 00:14:33.890
where you confessed.

00:14:34.850 --> 00:14:36.740
This feels just like a movie.

00:14:37.530 --> 00:14:42.060
At such an epic moment, shouldn't we...

00:14:59.210 --> 00:15:00.170
Tell me,

00:15:01.310 --> 00:15:02.910
what's the difference

00:15:03.830 --> 00:15:05.490
between friendship and love?

00:15:06.030 --> 00:15:07.330
Right now, it seems

00:15:07.720 --> 00:15:09.770
that except for kissing,

00:15:10.360 --> 00:15:12.090
nothing's changed between us.

00:15:15.720 --> 00:15:16.690
It's okay.

00:15:16.710 --> 00:15:18.270
We still have plenty of time

00:15:18.300 --> 00:15:19.560
to figure that out.

00:15:19.840 --> 00:15:20.520
Right?

00:15:24.260 --> 00:15:25.660
Then let's take our time!

00:15:31.120 --> 00:15:32.480
The thing between you and Ningn

00:15:32.480 --> 00:15:33.330
is over?

00:15:33.480 --> 00:15:34.050
Yeah.

00:15:34.330 --> 00:15:35.690
It caused such a scene,

00:15:35.690 --> 00:15:37.220
and you didn't even tell me.

00:15:38.560 --> 00:15:39.810
It wasn't a big deal.

00:15:40.930 --> 00:15:42.050
But I heard

00:15:42.050 --> 00:15:43.850
you passed Professor Ye's audition.

00:15:43.850 --> 00:15:44.240
Yeah.

00:15:45.970 --> 00:15:46.770
That's right.

00:15:47.210 --> 00:15:49.540
I attend Professor Ye's class every week.

00:15:51.090 --> 00:15:54.000
But Professor Ye said something to me.

00:15:54.030 --> 00:15:55.450
I didn't quite get it.

00:15:55.450 --> 00:15:56.170
What was it?

00:15:56.720 --> 00:15:57.720
Professor Ye said

00:15:57.720 --> 00:15:58.970
people in love

00:15:59.170 --> 00:16:00.530
could still break up.

00:16:00.570 --> 00:16:02.600
Why would people in love break up?

00:16:02.810 --> 00:16:03.850
I don't know.

00:16:04.210 --> 00:16:05.480
Why?

00:16:07.480 --> 00:16:08.400
Why?

00:16:09.170 --> 00:16:09.720
Shan.

00:16:10.150 --> 00:16:11.060
Why?

00:16:11.360 --> 00:16:13.210
Why do people in love break up?

00:16:14.480 --> 00:16:15.450
You don't get it.

00:16:15.970 --> 00:16:17.370
Let me ask you something.

00:16:17.480 --> 00:16:18.970
If you went abroad,

00:16:19.210 --> 00:16:20.590
