I shouldn't be with him now?

00:17:13.089 --> 00:17:13.960
Well,

00:17:14.089 --> 00:17:15.680
wait a second.

00:17:17.680 --> 00:17:18.849
What you're saying

00:17:18.849 --> 00:17:20.050
is just a hypothetical.

00:17:20.050 --> 00:17:21.680
I'm talking about the situation
when we're alive, which is different.

00:17:21.680 --> 00:17:23.810
What you're saying is also a hypothetical.

00:17:23.810 --> 00:17:25.440
Who can predict the future?

00:17:25.770 --> 00:17:26.490
So,

00:17:26.730 --> 00:17:28.190
if you love each other now,

00:17:28.490 --> 00:17:29.220
you should be

00:17:29.290 --> 00:17:30.730
together right now!

